{"nodes":[{"nodeID":"2689","text":"There is not any logical incompatibility between God and harm","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:43"},{"nodeID":"2690","text":"I don't think anyone has been able to show a logical incompatibility between God and harm.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:44"},{"nodeID":"2691","text":"this is very widely recognized by philosophers today.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:44"},{"nodeID":"2692","text":"Peter Van Inwagen of the University of Syracuse reports in the Philosophical Perspectives of 1991","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:44"},{"nodeID":"2693","text":"It used to be widely held that evil was incompatible with the existence of God: that no possible world contained both God and evil. So far as I am able tell this thesis is no longer defended.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:44"},{"nodeID":"2694","text":"Similarly William Alston a prominent philosopher says","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:44"},{"nodeID":"2695","text":"It is now acknowledged on (almost) all sides that the logical argument [from evil] is bankrupt.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:44"},{"nodeID":"2696","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:44"},{"nodeID":"2697","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:44"},{"nodeID":"2698","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:44","scheme":"Example","schemeID":"14"},{"nodeID":"2699","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:45","scheme":"Example","schemeID":"14"}],"edges":[{"edgeID":"2589","fromID":"2690","toID":"2696","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2590","fromID":"2696","toID":"2689","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2591","fromID":"2691","toID":"2697","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2592","fromID":"2697","toID":"2690","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2593","fromID":"2692","toID":"2698","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2594","fromID":"2693","toID":"2698","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2595","fromID":"2698","toID":"2691","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2596","fromID":"2694","toID":"2699","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2597","fromID":"2695","toID":"2699","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2598","fromID":"2699","toID":"2691","formEdgeID":null}],"locutions":[]}